data.description: Welcome to the Quail Run community! The open floor plan, cathedral ceilings, and large windows give this home a one of a kind charm that makes you want to settle in. The large windows let in lots of natural light and allows for a beautiful view of mature Oaks. The large family room offers great space for gatherings, and the bamboo flooring and fire place add to the elegant feel. The kitchen offers plenty of cabinetry and counter space, a breakfast nook, and a dining area with French doors leading to the back yard. All rooms are very generous in size and have ample closet space. The master bedroom offers a walk in closet and you will also find additional closet and storage space throughout this lovely home. The large backyard is great for entertaining or plenty of room for kids and pets to play. This home is located close to Shopping, Dining, Hospitals, UWF, I-10 and minutes away from the Pensacola airport. Call today for your private tour!
